<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zhǔ a nǐ yǒu yǒng shēng zhī dào 迦南1227</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ a nǐ yǒu yǒng shēng zhī dào, wǒ hái guī cóng shéi? zhǔ a nǐ yǒu yǒng shēng zhī dào, wǒ hái guī cóng shéi?
 shì shàng zài wú bié de shén, néng gěi wǒ rú cǐ ān wèi. nǐ de ài shì nà yàng de wán měi, wú
 lùn zǒu dào hé nián, fú shì nǐ yǒng bù hòu tuì. wú
 lùn yǒu duō shǎo kǎn kě, yǒng bù yáo dòng jǐn jǐn gēn suí. a nǐ yǒu
 yǒng shēng zhī dào, a wǒ hái guī cóng shéi? a nǐ yǒu yǒng shēng zhī dào,
 a wǒ hái guī cóng shéi?</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1227</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>